OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mainly
OL,6,Fcloudy evening and night with further
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain at times. Windy with
OL,8,Ffresh to strong southerly winds. A
OL,9,Fmilder night than last night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA mixture of bright or sunny
OL,12,Fintervals and occasional showers.
OL,13,FModerate to fresh southwesterly winds.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,16,FSunshine and scattered showers on
OL,17,FSaturday. Risk of rain on Sunday then
OL,18,Fdrier and brighter on Monday.
